#
# deploy API - InfoMetis controplane
#
# The deploy API consists of one method that executes the deployment phase.
#
# deploy [context] [up/down]
# deploy stack [up/down]    : fully deploy and run or shutdown and remove the container stack
# deploy module [up/down]   : fully deploy and run or shutdown and remove the container module
# deploy solution [up/down] : fully deploy and run or shutdown and remove the container solution
# See full reference for more details
#
# short notations:
# deploy          : deploy solution up
# deploy stack    : deploy stack up
# deploy module   : deploy module up
# deploy solution : deploy solution up
# remove          : deploy solution down
# remove stack    : deploy stack down
# remove module   : deploy module down
# remove solution : deploy solution down
#
